Class SmartCardErrors

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.panasonic.toughpad.android.api.smartcard.SmartCardErrors

  • public class SmartCardErrors
extends java.lang.Object
    SmartCardErrors This class defines error codes of method results.
    SmartCardReader.getLastError() uses these codes.
